Package: HAIgermany
Type: Package
Title: Shiny App for Exploring Healthcare-Associated Infection Data in Germany
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nathalie", "Aaes-JÃ¸rgensen", , "nathalie.aaesj@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny application for exploring the BHAI dataset of healthcare-associated infections in Germany (available in the R package 'BHAI'). 
    Users can visualize infection counts and patients at risk across age groups, select specific infection types, 
    and interpret the data through built-in explanatory text. This package includes preprocessed datasets 
    and functions to support the app without external data files.
